Since you updated to Play, it
downloads one at a time.

00:35:03.090 --> 00:35:04.780
So if you're downloading
like a one

00:35:04.780 --> 00:35:08.020
gigabyte, it takes forever.

00:35:08.020 --> 00:35:10.090
And the other one don't
download until

00:35:10.090 --> 00:35:12.042
the first ones finish.

00:35:12.042 --> 00:35:12.940
RICHARD: It's interesting.

00:35:12.940 --> 00:35:14.160
