it was faster than

00:35:42.670 --> 00:35:43.670
just one at a time.

00:35:43.670 --> 00:35:46.100
RICHARD: I guess the problem
with that is you end up--

00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:47.745
I don't know what the actual
problem was-- but you could

00:35:47.745 --> 00:35:49.450
end up with five apps finishing
at the same time,

00:35:49.450 --> 00:35:50.070
