00:35:52.625 --> 00:35:55.200
Because you can only be
installing one app at a time.

00:35:55.200 --> 00:35:57.660
But I didn't know that
had happened.

00:35:57.660 --> 00:36:01.135
MALE SPEAKER: It used to be one
